                <section class="comment-body"><p>Hello Chris,</p>
<p>it is in fact the other way around: Automation is possible for bypass, calibration byp, Mono monitoring and Plugin mode (could be more of course), but not the MIDI mapping. It is reproducable with V4 and V5. And I think I also tried with Reaper and did not succeed. But I am not that familiar with MIDI mapping in Reaper, so it could have been my fault. </p>
<p> </p></section>
              </div>

